T02D3049:94a-0: @94a * // dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3049:94a-1: rdo rje lhun po ri rab zom //
T02D3049:94a-2: rgyud do cog gi brgya rtsa brgyad //
T02D3049:94a-3: de yi rtsa bar 'di gsungs pa //
T02D3049:94b-0: @94b sgrub pa'i thabs ni brgya dang brgyad //
T02D3049:94b-2: 'di nyid la ni rnam pa gnyis //
T02D3049:94b-3: rgyud kyi rtsa ba gzhir blangs nas //
T02D3049:94b-4: bskyed pa nyid dang rdzogs pa'o //
T02D3049:94b-5: bskyed pa la ni brgya dang lnga //
T02D3049:94b-6: rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgrub pa gsum //
T02D3049:94b-8: de la thog mar dbang bskur ni //
T02D3049:94b-9: rten gyi gang zag smin bya'i phyir //
T02D3049:94b-11: dbang bskur rim pa gnyis su bshad //
T02D3049:94b-12: 'das pa la ni brgyad yin no //
T02D3049:94b-13: 'jig rten dbang bskur rnam pa drug / spyi yi dbang dang bco lnga yis //
T02D3049:94b-14: ma smin pa rnams smin par byed //
T02D3049:94b-15: de yi sngom ni 'di lta ste //
T02D3049:94b-16: de la sgrub thabs brgya dang brgyad gsungs pa la /
T02D3049:94b-17: 'jig rten 'di'i blo dor ba rnams la 'das pa'i dbang brgyad bskur te /
T02D3049:94b-18: blo rgya che ba spros pa la dga' ba rnams dang /
T02D3049:94b-19: lha sum cu rtsa lnga'i dkyil 'khor du dbang don gnyis rdzogs par 'dod pas /
T02D3049:94b-20: khro bo brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-21: las kyi sgrib pa rgyun gcod par 'dod pas /
T02D3049:94b-22: lha mo brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-24: khro bo bcu'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-25: rang gi don bsgrub par 'dod pas /
T02D3049:94b-26: dpa' bo gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ;
T02D3049:94b-28: yab yum gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-29: ye shes sngon du bsgrub par 'dod pas /
T02D3049:94b-30: rigs kyi khro bo lnga'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-31: mchog gi las bsgrub par 'dod pas /
T02D3049:94b-32: sgo ma bzhi'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur zhing bsnyen bsgrub bya'o //
T02D3049:94b-34: 'jig rten gyi 'dod pa nye bar 'dod pa rnams
T02D3049:94b-35: kyis 'jig rten pa'i dkyil 'khor drug tu dbang bskur
T02D3049:94b-36: te / 'jig rten pa'i mthu dang rdzu 'phrul 'dod pas phyogs skyong bcu'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-37: dpal dang dbang phyug 'dod pas rgyal po chen po bzhi'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-38: stobs dang grags pa 'dod bas gza' brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:94b-39: snyan pa dang legs par 'dod pas rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur /
T02D3049:95a-0: nad dang gdon zhi bar 'dod pas klu brgyal kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang @95a * //
T02D3049:95a-2: dbang bskur bcu bzhi po de dag gi las kyi
T02D3049:95a-3: rim pa la ston pa dbang bskur pa'i cho ga
T02D3049:95a-5: dbang bskur dam par gsol cig ces rgyud kyi sgrub par phyung ba'o //
T02D3049:95a-6: lhag ma gza'i las kyi bye brag bdun yod pa las /
T02D3049:95a-7: gza'i gdon las grol bar byed pa rin po che'i grol byed dang /
T02D3049:95a-8: gza' ngan pa bzlog pa rgya mtsho'i sprin dang /
T02D3049:95a-9: gza' brgyad kyi las ma grub pa grub par byed
T02D3049:95a-10: pa 'dod pa thams cad rab tu sbyin pa dang
T02D3049:95a-11: / bsgrub bya gza'i byad du gzhug pa'i 'khor lo can dang bcas pa dang /
T02D3049:95a-12: thog gis dgra bsad pa drag shul can dang /
T02D3049:95a-13: lo thog 'joms par byed pa chu thigs dang /
T02D3049:95a-14: 'gal ba skrag par byed pa'i las sna tshogs su bstan pa mgal me'i 'khor lo dang bdun la /
T02D3049:95a-16: rin po che grol byed dang /
T02D3049:95a-17: 'dod pa rab tu sbyin pa dang gsum mo //
T02D3049:95a-18: gza' dang zhes pa'i sgrub pa po 'khor lo can dang /
T02D3049:95a-20: chu thigs dang mgal me'i 'khor lo bzhi ni sems can thams cad skrag par byed pa'i bsgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95a-21: rgyu skar gyi gyi lhag ma gnyis la /
T02D3049:95a-22: rgyu skar ngan pa zlog par byed pa bdud rtsi sprin dang /
T02D3049:95a-23: rgyu skar gyi las sna tshogs sgrub par 'dod pa
T02D3049:95a-24: dus 'dzin bzang po dang gnyis ni rgyu skar dang
T02D3049:95a-26: lha brgyad kyi lhag ma gnyis la /
T02D3049:95a-27: 'jig rten pa'i lha nye bar byed pa don drug ni /
T02D3049:95a-28: lha rnams kyis phyogs pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95a-29: tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub ba dbul mo gter sbyin ni phongs pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95a-30: klu'i lhag ma brgyad las ya mas las thar bar byed pa yid bzhin nor bu dang /
T02D3049:95a-31: klu sgrub pa rin po che dbyig sgrub dang /
T02D3049:95a-32: klu gdon las grol par byed pa sgrul 'byin gsang ba dang /
T02D3049:95a-33: glu'i gdon las thar par byed pa klu srog me
T02D3049:95a-34: dpal gyi 'khor lo dang bzhi ni mi bzad gdon
T02D3049:95a-36: bsgrub bya phyang du gzhug pa'i srog gcod spu gri dang /
T02D3049:95a-37: rims kyis dgra bsad pa ral gri'i 'khor lo dang /
T02D3049:95a-38: rmugs pa'i las gzi mdangs chen mo dang gsum mo //
T02D3049:95a-39: sems can rmugs par byed pa'i las kyi mtha'o //
T02D3049:95a-40: char dbab pa bdud rtsi'i rgyun dang /
T02D3049:95b-0: chu gtor gyis klu la sogs pa'i gdon @95b rnams
T02D3049:95b-1: mnyes par byed ba bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho gnyis ni
T02D3049:95b-2: 'dod ba thams cad rab tu sbyin pa sgrub pa'o
T02D3049:95b-3: // ser ba srung ba 'byung brgyun gcod dang /
T02D3049:95b-4: byis pa gdon las thar bar byed pa me'i 'khor
T02D3049:95b-5: lo gnyis ni sems can thams cad srung bar byed
T02D3049:95b-6: pa'i sgrub pa'o // rdo rje rang rtags kyi sgrub pa bdun la /
T02D3049:95b-7: sgrub pa nges pa'i cho ga ni mi chod pa'i
T02D3049:95b-8: man ngag gi sgrub pa ni mi shigs pa'i sgrub
T02D3049:95b-9: ba'o // yo ga pra sen drag pa ni bden pa zhes ba'i sgrub ba'o //
T02D3049:95b-10: 'dod pa'i don dus la nges pa'i sgrub pa ni /
T02D3049:95b-11: sra ba zhes pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-12: dbang po dang ldan ba ni brtan ba zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-13: 'dod pa'i gtan tshigs thogs pa med pa ni /
T02D3049:95b-14: thogs pa med pa zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-17: pha rol gyi sde pham par byed pa dang /
T02D3049:95b-18: gdon dang nad las rgyal ba dad bzhi ni /
T02D3049:95b-19: thams cad du ma pham pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-20: mdon spyod kyi sbyin sreg ni sems can thams cad 'jil bar byed pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-22: rig sngags thams cad gcod par byed pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-23: ye shes 'dus pa'i tho ba ni /
T02D3049:95b-24: las thams cad 'joms par byed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-25: gser gyi ri bo ni rig sngags thams cad gnon par byed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-28: nye ba'i las phyi ma gsum ni gzhan gyi las thams cad 'jig par byed pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-29: lha'i gdon las thar bar byed pa dang /
T02D3049:95b-41: gnod sbyin gyi gdon las hthar bar byed pa dang bcu gsum ni /
T02D3049:95b-42: gdon thams cad las thar bar rbyed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-43: rdo rje tho ba ni gdon thams cad rlag par byed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-44: rdo rje lcags kyu ni 'byung po thams cad 'gugs par byed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-45: yid bzhin nor bu 'od 'bar ba ni /
T02D3049:95b-46: rig sngags kyi las thams cad byed du 'jug pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-47: rdo rje be con ni ma grub pa rnams grub par dbyed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-48: rin po che gter sgrub ni grub pa rnams chud mi za bar byed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:95b-49: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg ni zhi ba'o //
T02D3049:96a-2: rlung gi zhags pa gnyis ni sems can thams cad rengs par byed pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-4: dpal kun gyis ni legs par brgyan gyi sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-7: dri ma dang bral ba'i spyod byed dang /
T02D3049:96a-9: rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang lnga ni /
T02D3049:96a-10: sems can dbang po nyams pa dang zhes pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-12: bkra shis bum pa spyi blugs nas zhes pa'i sgrub ba'o //
T02D3049:96a-13: rab tu gnas pa ni bum pa'i kha rgyan dpag bsam shing zhes pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-15: dug bsal ba'i me long dang /
T02D3049:96a-16: rang byung 'jigs bral gsum ni tshe zad pa zhes pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-17: padma dbyig sgrub dang bcud len gnyis ni /
T02D3049:96a-18: tshe nyams dang zhes pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-19: dpag bsam sdong po dang rin po che las kyi phreng ba dang /
T02D3049:96a-20: las tshogs stong rgyas gsum ni /
T02D3049:96a-21: phun sum tshogs min gang chags dang ;
T02D3049:96a-24: gzhan gyi lce dbab pa bzlog pa dang /
T02D3049:96a-25: sdang ba gsum gyi las thor bu gsum ni /
T02D3049:96a-26: mdza' sdug skye bo sdang ba dang //
T02D3049:96a-29: bram ze la sogs gtses pa dang //
T02D3049:96a-31: rtsi sbyor dbyig gi nor bu ni /
T02D3049:96a-32: phan tshun mthun pa ma yin dang //
T02D3049:96a-34: dpag bsam kyi shing rgyas pa ni //
T02D3049:96a-35: nor 'gribs pas ni phongs pa dang //
T02D3049:96a-38: 'jigs pa dang ni gnod pa dang //
T02D3049:96a-40: phyir ldog 'khor lo ni byad stems dang zhes pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-42: srog chags dag ni thams cad kyi //
T02D3049:96a-43: mi bzad pa yi nad rnams kyang //
T02D3049:96a-45: rgyal mtshan rtse mo ni tshe 'phel pa'i sgrub pa'o //
T02D3049:96a-46: dpal ye shes phreng ba ni /
T02D3049:96a-48: de ltar brgya dang lnga ni /
T02D3049:96a-49: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i sgrub thabs so //
T02D3049:96a-50: sgra la gnas pa'i bsam gtan dang /
T02D3049:96a-51: sgra la mi gnas pa'i bsam gtan dang /
T02D3049:96a-52: sgra mthar gyis pa'i bsam gtan gsum ni /
T02D3049:96a-53: brab mo sangs rgyas spyod yul ba //
T02D3049:96a-55: them yig gsang ba zhes bya ba /
